*** This repository is no longer in use and not maintained. Archived for reference only. ***

Wordpress installation for FR2. Include wordpress core and custom ESI-based theme.

Run `cp config/wp-config.yml.sample config/wp-config.yml` and modify as necessary. 

Run `rake wordpress:options:load` to get the current options and `wordpress:options:dump` to dump changes you've made.

Config options that you want to always be loaded for this particular environment can be placed in config/wp-options.local.yml

Run `rake wordpress:update_core` to download the latest version of wordpress and install it locally
